{"tid":2495983,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Chill Club頒獎禮超級回味區 - Spotify playlist","createTime":"2021-04-19T13:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T02:08:57.000Z","uid":184592,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d46caf4305d7e804f8de5ef11c207bb58c4eca18","tid":2495983,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"今日忍唔住重J Chill Club頒獎禮多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲砌埋下面個playlist (總共63首歌):<br />\n<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/2p8RZruuWWRMREu0JzPoMT?si=0Q_97kWXR5WRlLHQgUza6w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fplaylist%2F2p8RZruuWWRMREu0JzPoMT%3Fsi%3D0Q_97kWXR5WRlLHQgUza6w&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=d2faa05f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://open.spotify.com/playlist/2p8RZruuWWRMREu0JzPoMT?si=0Q_97kWXR5WRlLHQgUza6w</a><br />\nPlaylist logic: 十大--&gt; 歌手獎--&gt; 表演項目--&gt; 新人 (重覆歌手盡量搵其他替代嘅歌)<br />\n<br />\n尋日好多歌都係聽幾句，不如認真聽下邊啲啱聽，<strong><span class=\"red\">最重要follow埋歌手嘅IG啦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>請2刷3刷頒獎禮，谷爆個view數</strong></span></strong></span>，等魯生下年批多啲budget，換個大場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://viu.tv/encore/chill-club-chart-award-presentation-2-0-21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2Fencore%2Fchill-club-chart-award-presentation-2-0-21&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=3565667c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://viu.tv/encore/chill-club-chart-award-presentation-2-0-21</a>"},{"pid":"b9382d3471ccffe0553c82aef01ae7209bd0b6e0","tid":2495983,"uid":30510,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:45:08.000Z","msg":"kkbox啦"},{"pid":"0bf384e42a1316e889e5b02077e21d7103432a18","tid":2495983,"uid":177630,"like"