0T02:00:07.000Z","msg":"好多謝你嘅留言支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afb54e8f1898cd9f3a8a4e010a7e4a8a24143e2","tid":2495983,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eae8cdc869983694fa4fcf058c971a5c62efe569","tid":2495983,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daf0a7f6c987086bc5f02a20b42041fafefc8ff0","tid":2495983,"uid":49544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T01:56:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無陳蕾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋重覆歌手無咩所謂，想揀曬D歌落去就最正，例如黃妍首我心中尚未崩壞的部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nANY肥多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T01:59:18.000Z","msg":"本身諗住太過重覆，所以冇加最開頭嗰段，我考慮吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:02:20.000Z","msg":"不過加嗰段就有東京人壽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af80c7615e4475ede6f4f19507f992b9c3ccaf42","tid":2495983,"uid":184592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:59:51.000Z","msg":"順便介紹返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQUhKMKAqsCr6NZdEyqdqKGMKjGa84bNpLKvLKK1uTEnT?filename=pvmfMQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvmfMQK.jpg&h=d1c692c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《2020年廣東歌精選 🇭🇰 香港本地音樂》總共分三Part<br />\n根據「叱咤樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮」及 @c_plus_music 十大作初步篩選&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n1️⃣Part 1大部份係年度之歌，入選唔單止計傳唱度，每首歌都有莫明嘅治癒感🫂<br />\n陪住香港人渡過創傷後遺及社交隔離😭<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n📍排名不分先後，小編靠直覺排序，只求loop得順耳👂🏻<br />\n📍特別揀選album version，方便大家link 去album發掘其他好歌🔎<br />\n📍好歌未能盡錄，請唔好每年關注樂壇一次，每月精選等緊你，尤其每月bonus track嘅indie音樂🎸<br />\n📍btw, 2018年精選已remake，2019年精選即將remake🛠<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><blockquote>許廷鏗 - 無力感<br />\nDear Jane - 銀河修理員<br />\n馮允謙 - 地球來的人<br />\n莫文蔚 - 呼吸有害<br />\n林家謙 - 一人之境<br />\nJer 柳應廷 - 水刑物語<br />\nRubberBand - First Date<br />\n陳健安 - 未知道<br />\n鄭中基 - My Only One<br />\nAGA 江海迦 - See You Next Time<br />\n陳奕迅 - 致明日的舞</blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n2️⃣Part 2大部份係主流樂壇之中嘅「另類👽」，雖則呢度講另類，喺外國其實唔算咩另類，只係香港人誤會廣東歌只得傳統曲式唧～💁🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n主流之中夾雜唔同曲風，某啲歌單獨聽可能古怪，但放入playlist突然變得啱數，耳仔接受能力慢慢就會擴闊👂🏻，亦都係小編砌playlist嘅策略🤖<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n📍排名不分先後，小編靠直覺排序，只求loop得順耳👂🏻<br />\n📍特別揀選album version，方便大家link 去album發掘其他好歌🔎<br />\n📍好歌未能盡錄，請唔好每年關注樂壇一次，每月精選等緊你，尤其每月bonus track嘅indie音樂🎸<br />\n📍btw, 2018年精選已remake，2019年精選即將remake🛠<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><blockquote>馮允謙 - 開始倒數<br />\nRubberBand - 百毒不侵<br />\n陳蕾 - 娑婆<br />\n岑寧兒 - 困局<br />\n許廷鏗 - Negative<br />\n陳柏宇 - 感情這回事<br />\n黃妍 - 牆身有裂<br />\n衛蘭 - 帶走你的垃圾<br />\nper se - 粉碎糖果屋 (feat. Serrini)<br />\nSerrini - 網絡安全隱患<br />\n林家謙 - 特倫斯夢遊仙境<br />\nMirror - IGNITED</blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n3️⃣Part 3嘅歌單，集合2020年 &quot;不能遺忘&quot; 嘅作品💆🏻<br />\n部份係令人期待嘅new voice...出道幾年我都叫🆕<br />\n部份歌手喺Part 1, 2出現過，因為作品俱代表性，要再次入選先可以完整展現2020香港本地音樂～🎖<br />\n <br />\n<span class=\"small\"><blockquote>Nowhere Boys - 最後的搖滾<br />\nDear Jane - 最後一間唱片舖<br />\nDusty Bottle - Break It Down<br />\nJace 陳凱詠 - 天生二品<br />\n馮允謙 - 愛斯基摩人之吻<br />\n林家謙 - 拼命無恙<br />\nGin Lee 李幸倪 - 幸福門<br />\n黎曉陽 - 阿茲與海默<br />\n姜濤 - 蒙著嘴說愛你<br />\nError - 我們很帥<br />\nSerrini - ~旋轉with me*<br />\n泳兒 - 溝渠暢泳<br />\nJuno 麥浚龍, 謝安琪 - 合唱歌</blockquote></span>"},{"pid":"266c023b533adc4c286bd360097c2d848becead0","tid":2495983,"uid":184592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"orange\">2019, 2018 精選</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"red\"><strong>2019精選</strong></span><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.kfs.io/playlist/global/63595201v8/fit/500x500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http